#: ../../developer/general/gsoc.rst:204 c89bcda999424f319fb8b56cbc1c71cf
msgid ""
"**Brief explanation**: Large number of VMs is hard to maintain. Templates "
"helps with keeping them updated, but many applications have configuration in"
" user home directory, which is not synchronized."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/gsoc.rst:208 647d441bc38a4519be13711abec5522d
msgid ""
"Design a mechanism how to *safely* synchronize application configuration "
"living in user home directory (``~/.config``, some other “dotfiles”). "
"Mechanism should be resistant against malicious VM forcing its configuration"
" on other VMs. Some approach could be a strict control which VM can send "
"what changes (whitelist approach, not blacklist)."
msgstr ""

